-- French Nationals Taken Hostage in Cameroon, Hollande Says
-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 2013-02-19T14:32:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-19/french-nationals-taken-hostage-in-cameroon-hollande-says.html
Seven French citizens have been
taken hostage in Cameroon, President Francois Hollande told
journalists in Athens.  The hostages included three adults and four children,
Hollande said. French authorities are familiar with the
terrorist group, which is based in Nigeria, he added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
